{"tid":1722664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬引特權法設委員會查反修例因由","createTime":"2019-11-15T03:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T04:04:57.000Z","uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0372ffaae0285db485df8346b02f7e171906586f","tid":1722664,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"經民聯立法會議員梁美芬本月27日動議引用《立法會(權力及特權)條例》，成立專責委員會調查反修例風波，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">獲立法會主席梁君彥批准</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n議案指出，示威及騷亂致香港的法治、社會秩序、民生及經濟受到嚴重影響，建議專責委員會調查騷亂的前因後果，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">是否有外部勢力干預，以及資金及物資來源，尋找引起騷亂的深層次矛盾，並研究解決方法</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2304916/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2304916%2F&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=5c8967d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2304916/</a>"},{"pid":"76a95045ccd93e260c02d7f4e7ea707d1633b3e9","tid":1722664,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:09:15.000Z","msg":"咁引特權法查班狗官同班狗"},{"pid":"9367bb7524c2bcc2cbd14065327f49ed2940cd12","tid":1722664,"uid":181747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"預測結果<br />\n1.是<br />\n2.美國<br />\n3.房屋問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1320e11c28362d06e57d68fca7f563720db3281e","tid":1722664,"uid":312598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9367bb7524c2bcc2cbd14065327f49ed2940cd12","tid":1722664,"uid":181747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"預測結果<br />\n1.是<br />\n2.美國<br />\n3.房屋問題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s